    ''' ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    ''' <summary>
    ''' A plugin that handles the bot behavior when the server gets down. 
    ''' <para></para>
    ''' Note that it ﻿does not ﻿handle ﻿lag, ﻿local network inactivity﻿﻿ neither ﻿authentication connection problems.
    ''' </summary>
    ''' ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    ''' <seealso cref="Plugin"/>
    ''' ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
